<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRIME PREVENTION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Why can't Republicans comprehend the fact that crime is nurtured by 
prohibition and starved by education? 
</P>
<P>
 WALTER L. ROSS 
</P>
<P>
 Fallbrook 
</P>
