<DOCNO> LA092294-0252 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 081630 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 22, 1994, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
