<HEADLINE>
<P>
CITY HALL JOURNAL: CERRITOS; ENGINEER APPOINTED TO PLANNING COMMISSION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN CANALIS 
</P>
